{
  "stem": "14737.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The spelling of Dolha has different spelling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Actually, they call it Dolha, however in the Russian it is Dovhoje or how they spell it there is Dolgoye.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So if you look somewhere places, you may find under the name Dolha, Dolgoye or Dovhoje.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, this is small little town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's important because has a crossroads.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In other words, from that little town, from Dolha, you can go three different direction to larger cities, like Khust, Beregsaz, Munkacs, or even to Svalyava.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The population in Dolha is the following.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1944, there were approximately 110 Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, there lived a lot of non-Jewish families, mostly Carpatho-Russians, Ukrainians, and other minorities also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't exactly in numbers to say the population.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The, the houses were approximately 800.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, figure out that in every household, there are four, five, six children, so I would say approximately maybe close to 4,000.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Today, I don't know how much is there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Dolha, mostly, most of the thing that lived there were Ukranians, Russians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they lived there already for centuries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shall I tell you, when I was born, there was illiteracy approximately 95% percent, if not more, among people-- not among Jews, but among the other.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they didn't go to school in the Hungarian regime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even now, during, during the regime of Czechoslovakia, to send a child to school was-- they needed the child for something else or some other purpose, especially the non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They needed the child to go with the cow or somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's only when it was so obligatory that they were punished or something, they were put fines, so they did send the child to a school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Naturally, the school was very primitive.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
